PrecisRe-appointment of YVON TARTE, of Ottawa, Ontario, as Chairperson of the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of two years; and orders that YVON TARTE shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective May 7, 2001.
